description: There's nothing like a hot dog cart  when you're craving great grub on the go! Sparky's Hot Dogs is serving up the classic hot dogs you know and love. Made with quality ingredients and packed with flavor, these are hot dogs you'll love from the very first bite! When you're looking for the best of the best on the streets of Sheboygan, there's nobody like Sparky's Hot Dogs!
name: Sparky's Hot Dogs
